{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":717,"text":"I was on a long road trip this summer,"},{"time":3167,"text":"and I was having\na wonderful time listening"},{"time":6245,"text":"to the amazing Isabel Wilkerson's\n\"The Warmth of Other Suns.\""},{"time":10992,"text":"It documents six million black folks\nfleeing the South from 1915 to 1970"},{"time":20761,"text":"looking for a respite\nfrom all the brutality"},{"time":24238,"text":"and trying to get to a better\nopportunity up North,"},{"time":27999,"text":"and it was filled with stories\nof the resilience and the brilliance"},{"time":32407,"text":"of African-Americans,"},{"time":34362,"text":"and it was also really hard to hear\nall the stories of the horrors"},{"time":38731,"text":"\nand the humility,\nand all the humiliations."},{"time":44320,"text":"It was especially hard to hear\nabout the beatings and the burnings"},{"time":49029,"text":"and the lynchings of black men."},{"time":51366,"text":"And I said, \"You know,\nthis is a little deep."},{"time":54632,"text":"I need a break. I'm going\nto turn on the radio.\""},{"time":58915,"text":"I turned it on, and there it was:"},{"time":62061,"text":"Ferguson, Missouri,"},{"time":64233,"text":"Michael Brown,"},{"time":66445,"text":"18-year-old black man,"},{"time":68665,"text":"unarmed, shot by a white police officer,\nlaid on the ground dead,"},{"time":74564,"text":"blood running for four hours"},{"time":78478,"text":"while his grandmother and little children\nand his neighbors watched in horror,"},{"time":82993,"text":"and I thought,"},{"time":86019,"text":"here it is again."},{"time":89240,"text":"This violence, this brutality\nagainst black men"},{"time":92962,"text":"has been going on for centuries."},{"time":95824,"text":"I mean, it's the same story.\nIt's just different names."},{"time":100396,"text":"It could have been Amadou Diallo."},{"time":104498,"text":"It could have been Sean Bell."},{"time":106823,"text":"It could have been Oscar Grant."},{"time":110213,"text":"It could have been Trayvon Martin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114205,"text":"This violence, this brutality,"},{"time":117044,"text":"is really something that's part\nof our national psyche."},{"time":119863,"text":"It's part of our collective history."},{"time":122632,"text":"What are we going to do about it?"},{"time":127447,"text":"You know that part of us that still\ncrosses the street,"},{"time":132672,"text":"locks the doors,"},{"time":134722,"text":"clutches the purses,"},{"time":137076,"text":"when we see young black men?"},{"time":139962,"text":"That part."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142023,"text":"I mean, I know we're not\nshooting people down in the street,"},{"time":145971,"text":"but I'm saying that the same\nstereotypes and prejudices"},{"time":150058,"text":"that fuel those kinds of tragic incidents\n"},{"time":153123,"text":"are in us."},{"time":155328,"text":"We've been schooled in them as well."},{"time":159195,"text":"I believe that we can stop\nthese types of incidents,"},{"time":165758,"text":"these Fergusons from happening,"},{"time":168729,"text":"by looking within\nand being willing to change ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174078,"text":"So I have a call to action for you."},{"time":177369,"text":"There are three things that I want\nto offer us today to think about"},{"time":181454,"text":"as ways to stop Ferguson\nfrom happening again;"},{"time":186562,"text":"three things that I think will help us"},{"time":188861,"text":"reform our images of young black men;"},{"time":192336,"text":"three things that I'm hoping\nwill not only protect them"},{"time":196652,"text":"but will open the world\nso that they can thrive."},{"time":200848,"text":"Can you imagine that?"},{"time":203149,"text":"Can you imagine our country\nembracing young black men,"},{"time":207700,"text":"seeing them as part of our future,\ngiving them that kind of openness,"},{"time":213045,"text":"that kind of grace we give\nto people we love?"},{"time":216758,"text":"How much better would our lives be?\nHow much better would our country be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221054,"text":"Let me just start with number one."},{"time":223967,"text":"We gotta get out of denial."},{"time":228956,"text":"Stop trying to be good people."},{"time":231359,"text":"We need real people."},{"time":233503,"text":"You know, I do a lot of diversity work,"},{"time":235412,"text":"and people will come up to me\nat the beginning of the workshop."},{"time":238382,"text":"They're like, \"Oh, Ms. Diversity Lady,\nwe're so glad you're here\" --"},{"time":242067,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":243646,"text":"\"but we don't have a biased bone \nin our body.\""},{"time":246659,"text":"And I'm like, \"Really?"},{"time":248522,"text":"Because I do this work every day,\nand I see all my biases.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":253010,"text":"I mean, not too long ago, I was on a plane"},{"time":256525,"text":"and I heard the voice of a woman\npilot coming over the P.A. system,"},{"time":260902,"text":"and I was just so excited, so thrilled."},{"time":263014,"text":"I was like, \"Yes, women,\nwe are rocking it."},{"time":266116,"text":"We are now in the stratosphere.\""},{"time":268326,"text":"It was all good, and then it started\ngetting turbulent and bumpy,"},{"time":271460,"text":"and I was like,"},{"time":272877,"text":"\"I hope she can drive.\""},{"time":275295,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":276634,"text":"I know. Right."},{"time":277826,"text":"But it's not even like\nI knew that was a bias"},{"time":280068,"text":"until I was coming back on the other leg\nand there's always a guy driving"},{"time":283558,"text":"and it's often turbulent and bumpy,"},{"time":285307,"text":"and I've never questioned\nthe confidence of the male driver."},{"time":288133,"text":"The pilot is good."},{"time":290089,"text":"Now, here's the problem."},{"time":292585,"text":"If you ask me explicitly,\nI would say, \"Female pilot: awesome.\""},{"time":300096,"text":"But it appears that when things get funky\nand a little troublesome, a little risky,"},{"time":304792,"text":"I lean on a bias that I didn't\neven know that I had."},{"time":308802,"text":"You know, fast-moving planes in the sky,"},{"time":311416,"text":"I want a guy."},{"time":313379,"text":"That's my default."},{"time":315662,"text":"Men are my default."},{"time":318291,"text":"Who is your default?"},{"time":320611,"text":"Who do you trust?"},{"time":322641,"text":"Who are you afraid of?"},{"time":324774,"text":"Who do you implicitly feel connected to?"},{"time":328805,"text":"Who do you run away from?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331847,"text":"I'm going to tell you\nwhat we have learned."},{"time":334271,"text":"The implicit association test,\nwhich measures unconscious bias,"},{"time":339669,"text":"you can go online and take it."},{"time":341389,"text":"Five million people have taken it."},{"time":343645,"text":"Turns out, our default is white.\nWe like white people."},{"time":349555,"text":"We prefer white. What do I mean by that?"},{"time":352315,"text":"When people are shown images \nof black men and white men,"},{"time":357569,"text":"we are more quickly able to associate"},{"time":361562,"text":"that picture with a positive word,\nthat white person with a positive word,"},{"time":365640,"text":"than we are when we are \ntrying to associate"},{"time":368305,"text":"positive with a black face,\nand vice versa."},{"time":372010,"text":"When we see a black face,"},{"time":373900,"text":"it is easier for us to connect\nblack with negative"},{"time":379948,"text":"than it is white with negative."},{"time":382075,"text":"Seventy percent of white people\ntaking that test prefer white."},{"time":389039,"text":"Fifty percent of black people\ntaking that test prefer white."},{"time":393753,"text":"You see, we were all outside\nwhen the contamination came down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399310,"text":"What do we do about the fact\nthat our brain automatically associates?"},{"time":405697,"text":"You know, one of the things\nthat you probably are thinking about,"},{"time":411306,"text":"and you're probably like, you know what,"},{"time":413284,"text":"I'm just going to double down\non my color blindness."},{"time":416818,"text":"Yes, I'm going to recommit to that."},{"time":418545,"text":"I'm going to suggest to you, no."},{"time":420662,"text":"We've gone about as far as we can go\ntrying to make a difference"},{"time":423821,"text":"trying to not see color."},{"time":425434,"text":"The problem was never that we saw color.\nIt was what we did when we saw the color."},{"time":430269,"text":"It's a false ideal."},{"time":434270,"text":"And while we're busy \npretending not to see,"},{"time":437040,"text":"we are not being aware of the ways\nin which racial difference"},{"time":440871,"text":"is changing people's possibilities,\nthat's keeping them from thriving,"},{"time":446152,"text":"and sometimes it's causing them\nan early death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451339,"text":"So in fact, what the scientists\nare telling us is, no way."},{"time":456885,"text":"Don't even think about color blindness."},{"time":459280,"text":"In fact, what they're suggesting is,"},{"time":461760,"text":"stare at awesome black people."},{"time":466290,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":468030,"text":"Look at them directly in their faces\nand memorize them,"},{"time":472997,"text":"because when we look\nat awesome folks who are black,"},{"time":477663,"text":"it helps to dissociate"},{"time":480872,"text":"the association that happens\nautomatically in our brain."},{"time":486405,"text":"Why do you think I'm showing you\nthese beautiful black men behind me?"},{"time":491827,"text":"There were so many, I had to cut them."},{"time":495039,"text":"Okay, so here's the thing:"},{"time":496351,"text":"I'm trying to reset your automatic\nassociations about who black men are."},{"time":502279,"text":"I'm trying to remind you"},{"time":504641,"text":"that young black men\ngrow up to be amazing human beings"},{"time":509665,"text":"who have changed our lives\nand made them better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515371,"text":"So here's the thing."},{"time":517890,"text":"The other possibility in science,"},{"time":520441,"text":"and it's only temporarily changing\nour automatic assumptions,"},{"time":523365,"text":"but one thing we know"},{"time":525870,"text":"is that if you take a white person\nwho is odious that you know,"},{"time":530662,"text":"and stick it up next to a person of color,"},{"time":533672,"text":"a black person, who is fabulous,"},{"time":536131,"text":"then that sometimes actually\ncauses us to disassociate too."},{"time":539637,"text":"So think Jeffrey Dahmer and Colin Powell."},{"time":544851,"text":"Just stare at them, right? (Laughter)"},{"time":547359,"text":"But these are the things.\nSo go looking for your bias."},{"time":550168,"text":"Please, please, just get out of denial\nand go looking for disconfirming data"},{"time":554257,"text":"that will prove that in fact\nyour old stereotypes are wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":558847,"text":"Okay, so that's number one: number two,"},{"time":560781,"text":"what I'm going to say is move toward\nyoung black men instead of away from them."},{"time":565466,"text":"It's not the hardest thing to do,"},{"time":568058,"text":"but it's also one of these things"},{"time":571928,"text":"where you have to be conscious \nand intentional about it."},{"time":574604,"text":"You know, I was in a Wall Street area \none time several years ago"},{"time":577712,"text":"when I was with a colleague of mine,\nand she's really wonderful"},{"time":581094,"text":"and she does diversity work with me\nand she's a woman of color, she's Korean."},{"time":584734,"text":"And we were outside,\nit was late at night,"},{"time":586684,"text":"and we were sort of wondering where\nwe were going, we were lost."},{"time":589726,"text":"And I saw this person across the street,\nand I was thinking, \"Oh great, black guy.\""},{"time":593910,"text":"I was going toward him\nwithout even thinking about it."},{"time":596678,"text":"And she was like,\n\"Oh, that's interesting.\""},{"time":600462,"text":"The guy across the street,\nhe was a black guy."},{"time":603280,"text":"I think black guys generally\nknow where they're going."},{"time":606939,"text":"I don't know why exactly I think that,\nbut that's what I think."},{"time":610584,"text":"So she was saying, \"Oh, you\nwere going, 'Yay, a black guy'?\""},{"time":615925,"text":"She said, \"I was going,\n'Ooh, a black guy.'\""},{"time":618989,"text":"Other direction. Same need,\nsame guy, same clothes,\n"},{"time":622385,"text":"same time, same street,\ndifferent reaction."},{"time":625734,"text":"And she said, \"I feel so bad.\nI'm a diversity consultant."},{"time":628463,"text":"I did the black guy thing.\nI'm a woman of color. Oh my God!\""},{"time":631281,"text":"And I said, \"You know what? Please.\nWe really need to relax about this.\""},{"time":635055,"text":"I mean, you've got to realize\nI go way back with black guys."},{"time":638781,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":641527,"text":"My dad is a black guy.\nYou see what I'm saying?"},{"time":644763,"text":"I've got a 6'5\" black guy son.\nI was married to a black guy."},{"time":648703,"text":"My black guy thing\nis so wide and so deep"},{"time":651219,"text":"that I can pretty much sort\nand figure out who that black guy is,"},{"time":656009,"text":"and he was my black guy."},{"time":657959,"text":"He said, \"Yes, ladies, I know\nwhere you're going. I'll take you there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":661733,"text":"You know, biases are the stories\nwe make up about people"},{"time":665376,"text":"before we know who they actually are."},{"time":667888,"text":"But how are we going to know who they are"},{"time":670620,"text":"when we've been told to avoid\nand be afraid of them?"},{"time":674427,"text":"So I'm going to tell you\nto walk toward your discomfort."},{"time":679480,"text":"And I'm not asking you\nto take any crazy risks."},{"time":682517,"text":"I'm saying, just do an inventory,"},{"time":687417,"text":"expand your social\nand professional circles."},{"time":691309,"text":"Who's in your circle?"},{"time":693139,"text":"Who's missing?"},{"time":695635,"text":"How many authentic relationships"},{"time":699592,"text":"do you have with young black people,\nfolks, men, women?"},{"time":706062,"text":"Or any other major difference\nfrom who you are"},{"time":709814,"text":"and how you roll, so to speak?"},{"time":713150,"text":"Because, you know what?\nJust look around your periphery."},{"time":716229,"text":"There may be somebody at work,\nin your classroom,"},{"time":718532,"text":"in your house of worship, somewhere,\nthere's some black young guy there."},{"time":721980,"text":"And you're nice. You say hi."},{"time":723438,"text":"I'm saying go deeper, closer, further,\nand build the kinds of relationships,"},{"time":729784,"text":"the kinds of friendships that actually\ncause you to see the holistic person"},{"time":735064,"text":"and to really go against the stereotypes."},{"time":738552,"text":"I know some of you are out there,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":740145,"text":"\nI know because I have some white\nfriends in particular that will say,"},{"time":743436,"text":"\"You have no idea how awkward I am."},{"time":745408,"text":"Like, I don't think this\nis going to work for me."},{"time":748140,"text":"I'm sure I'm going to blow this.\""},{"time":749876,"text":"Okay, maybe, but this thing is not \nabout perfection. It's about connection."},{"time":755835,"text":"And you're not going to get comfortable\nbefore you get uncomfortable."},{"time":760839,"text":"I mean, you just have to do it."},{"time":762969,"text":"And young black men, what I'm saying is"},{"time":765316,"text":"if someone comes your way, genuinely\nand authentically, take the invitation."},{"time":770361,"text":"Not everyone is out to get you."},{"time":772211,"text":"Go looking for those people\nwho can see your humanity."},{"time":776691,"text":"You know, it's the empathy\nand the compassion"},{"time":780199,"text":"that comes out of having relationships\nwith people who are different from you."},{"time":784903,"text":"Something really powerful\nand beautiful happens:"},{"time":787898,"text":"you start to realize that they are you,"},{"time":790414,"text":"that they are part of you,\nthat they are you in your family,"},{"time":796196,"text":"and then we cease to be bystanders"},{"time":799194,"text":"and we become actors,\nwe become advocates,"},{"time":803179,"text":"and we become allies."},{"time":805677,"text":"So go away from your comfort\ninto a bigger, brighter thing,"},{"time":811148,"text":"because that is how we will stop\nanother Ferguson from happening."},{"time":816140,"text":"That's how we create a community"},{"time":818370,"text":"where everybody, especially\nyoung black men, can thrive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":821382,"text":"So this last thing is going to be harder,"},{"time":824305,"text":"and I know it, but I'm just going\nto put it out there anyway."},{"time":827173,"text":"When we see something, we have to have\nthe courage to say something,"},{"time":832412,"text":"even to the people we love."},{"time":836206,"text":"You know, it's holidays\nand it's going to be a time"},{"time":839847,"text":"when we're sitting around the table\nand having a good time."},{"time":843279,"text":"Many of us, anyways, will be in holidays,"},{"time":845478,"text":"and you've got to listen to\nthe conversations around the table."},{"time":850402,"text":"You start to say things like,\n\"Grandma's a bigot.\""},{"time":857094,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":858924,"text":"\"Uncle Joe is racist.\""},{"time":861863,"text":"And you know, we love Grandma\nand we love Uncle Joe. We do."},{"time":866482,"text":"We know they're good people,\nbut what they're saying is wrong."},{"time":873317,"text":"And we need to be able to say something,\nbecause you know who else is at the table?"},{"time":880300,"text":"The children are at the table."},{"time":883154,"text":"And we wonder why these biases don't die,\nand move from generation to generation?"},{"time":888399,"text":"Because we're not saying anything."},{"time":891650,"text":"We've got to be willing to say, \"Grandma,\nwe don't call people that anymore.\""},{"time":898172,"text":"\"Uncle Joe, it isn't true\nthat he deserved that."},{"time":903383,"text":"No one deserves that.\""},{"time":906319,"text":"And we've got to be willing"},{"time":909733,"text":"to not shelter our children\nfrom the ugliness of racism"},{"time":914507,"text":"when black parents don't\nhave the luxury to do so,"},{"time":917819,"text":"especially those who have \nyoung black sons."},{"time":922600,"text":"We've got to take \nour lovely darlings, our future,"},{"time":925981,"text":"and we've got to tell them we have \nan amazing country with incredible ideals,"},{"time":933783,"text":"we have worked incredibly hard,\nand we have made some progress,"},{"time":936762,"text":"but we are not done."},{"time":939932,"text":"We still have in us this old stuff"},{"time":943926,"text":"about superiority and it is causing us"},{"time":946967,"text":"to embed those further\ninto our institutions"},{"time":950439,"text":"and our society and generations,"},{"time":952418,"text":"and it is making for despair"},{"time":956027,"text":"and disparities and a devastating\ndevaluing of young black men."},{"time":963151,"text":"We still struggle, you have to tell them,"},{"time":965612,"text":"with seeing both the color"},{"time":968390,"text":"and the character of young black men,"},{"time":972024,"text":"but that you, and you expect them,"},{"time":975857,"text":"to be part of the forces of change\nin this society"},{"time":980371,"text":"that will stand against injustice\nand is willing, above all other things,"},{"time":986939,"text":"to make a society where young black men \ncan be seen for all of who they are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996705,"text":"So many amazing black men,"},{"time":1001627,"text":"those who are the most amazing\nstatesmen that have ever lived,"},{"time":1009959,"text":"brave soldiers,"},{"time":1012992,"text":"awesome, hardworking laborers."},{"time":1017286,"text":"These are people who\nare powerful preachers."},{"time":1021942,"text":"They are incredible scientists\nand artists and writers."},{"time":1027537,"text":"They are dynamic comedians."},{"time":1031512,"text":"They are doting grandpas,"},{"time":1036448,"text":"caring sons."},{"time":1039480,"text":"They are strong fathers,"},{"time":1044237,"text":"and they are young men\nwith dreams of their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048593,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052150,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}